{
  "id": "RAW_7d5b45",
  "title": "Vercel Chat SDK 发布",
  "url": "https://vercel.com/blog/introducing-chat-sdk",
  "date": "2025-04-09 13:00:00",
  "author": "Jared Palmer, Jeremy Philemon",
  "siteName": "Vercel News",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack article_content__xNUGz\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:center;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:24px\" data-customer-story=\"false\">\n   <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack article_dateAndTimeToRead__6RnTk\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:row;--stack-align:center;--stack-justify:space-between;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:0px\">\n    <div class=\"flex items-center gap-x-2 sm:gap-x-6\">\n     <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:row;--stack-align:center;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:6px\">\n      <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-900);--text-size:0.875rem;--text-line-height:1.25rem;--text-letter-spacing:0px;--text-weight:400\"><br></p></div></div></div>\n   <div class=\"article_leadIn__vSmkA\">\n    <p>Chat SDK is a free, open-source template for building powerful chatbot applications.</p>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">The <a href=\"https://sdk.vercel.ai/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">AI SDK</a> powers <a href=\"https://sdk.vercel.ai/showcase\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">incredible applications</a> across the web, and today we're excited to announce the <a href=\"https://chat-sdk.dev\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">Chat SDK</a> - the best-in-class, production-ready template for building conversational AI applications like ChatGPT or Claude artifacts.</p>\n   <figure class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack blog-media_media__17gkA\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:center;--stack-justify:center;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:16px\">\n    <img data-version=\"v1\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"900\" height=\"471\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"image_intrinsic__ulrJk blog-mode-dependent-media_addPadding__lfHNN blog-mode-dependent-media_notScreenshot__QVv9c image_lightMode__SmqSs\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcset=\"https://assets.vercel.com/image/upload/contentful/image/e5382hct74si/OWxoUSnXxkTZWzrPb53g9/0c3c8590c069dd998c4b1abb3ff500d3/chat-sdk-og-light.png, https://assets.vercel.com/image/upload/contentful/image/e5382hct74si/OWxoUSnXxkTZWzrPb53g9/0c3c8590c069dd998c4b1abb3ff500d3/chat-sdk-og-light.png\" src=\"https://assets.vercel.com/image/upload/contentful/image/e5382hct74si/OWxoUSnXxkTZWzrPb53g9/0c3c8590c069dd998c4b1abb3ff500d3/chat-sdk-og-light.png\">\n   </figure>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">With the Chat SDK, you get a complete production-ready application built on <a href=\"https://nextjs.org/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">Next.js</a> App Router with the <a href=\"https://sdk.vercel.ai\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">AI SDK</a> at its core, allowing you to use any AI model and provider throughout your application. It leverages the best patterns we've developed and learned from building <a href=\"https://v0.dev/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">v0</a>, and it's always up to date with the latest advancements. Built on strong foundations -- message persistence, authentication, multimodal support, and shareable chats -- the Chat SDK differentiates itself with powerful features like generative UI, customizable artifacts, and in-browser code execution.</p>\n   <figure class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack blog-media_media__17gkA blog-video-asset_videoWrapper__RSAt5 geist-show-on-light-theme\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:center;--stack-justify:center;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:16px\">\n    <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack blog-media_outside__8KjIr blog-video-asset_videoBorder__Kuumi\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"aspect-ratio:1600/900;--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:stretch;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:0px\">\n     <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack blog-media_inside__Mq7tv\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:stretch;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:0px\">\n      <figure class=\"video_figure__rlLg4 video_oversize__n2jkl\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--video-margin:0px;--video-width:min(1600px, 950px)\">\n       <div class=\"video_main__8vED4\" style=\"width:100%;\"></div>\n      </figure>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </figure>\n   <figure class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack blog-media_media__17gkA blog-video-asset_videoWrapper__RSAt5 geist-show-on-dark-theme\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:center;--stack-justify:center;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:16px\">\n    <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack blog-media_outside__8KjIr blog-video-asset_videoBorder__Kuumi\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"aspect-ratio:1600/900;--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:stretch;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:0px\">\n     <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack blog-media_inside__Mq7tv\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:stretch;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:0px\">\n      <figure class=\"video_figure__rlLg4 video_oversize__n2jkl\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--video-margin:0px;--video-width:min(1600px, 950px)\">\n       <div class=\"video_main__8vED4\" style=\"width:100%;\"></div>\n      </figure>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </figure>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">With generative UI, you can create dynamic, interactive interfaces that go beyond simple text responses, enabling rich user experiences that adapt to the conversation context.</p>\n   <figure class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack blog-media_media__17gkA blog-video-asset_videoWrapper__RSAt5 geist-show-on-light-theme\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:center;--stack-justify:center;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:16px\">\n    <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack blog-media_outside__8KjIr blog-video-asset_videoBorder__Kuumi\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"aspect-ratio:1600/900;--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:stretch;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:0px\">\n     <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack blog-media_inside__Mq7tv\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:stretch;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:0px\">\n      <figure class=\"video_figure__rlLg4 video_oversize__n2jkl\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--video-margin:0px;--video-width:min(1600px, 950px)\">\n       <div class=\"video_main__8vED4\" style=\"width:100%;\"></div>\n      </figure>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </figure>\n   <figure class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack blog-media_media__17gkA blog-video-asset_videoWrapper__RSAt5 geist-show-on-dark-theme\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:center;--stack-justify:center;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:16px\">\n    <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack blog-media_outside__8KjIr blog-video-asset_videoBorder__Kuumi\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"aspect-ratio:1600/900;--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:stretch;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:0px\">\n     <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack blog-media_inside__Mq7tv\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:stretch;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:0px\">\n      <figure class=\"video_figure__rlLg4 video_oversize__n2jkl\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--video-margin:0px;--video-width:min(1600px, 950px)\">\n       <div class=\"video_main__8vED4\" style=\"width:100%;\"></div>\n      </figure>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </figure>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Custom artifacts allow you to build specialized components tailored to your specific use cases, from document creation to interactive tools that enhance the functionality of your chatbot.</p>\n   <figure class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack blog-media_media__17gkA blog-video-asset_videoWrapper__RSAt5 geist-show-on-light-theme\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:center;--stack-justify:center;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:16px\">\n    <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack blog-media_outside__8KjIr blog-video-asset_videoBorder__Kuumi\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"aspect-ratio:1600/900;--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:stretch;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:0px\">\n     <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack blog-media_inside__Mq7tv\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:stretch;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:0px\">\n      <figure class=\"video_figure__rlLg4 video_oversize__n2jkl\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--video-margin:0px;--video-width:min(1600px, 950px)\">\n       <div class=\"video_main__8vED4\" style=\"width:100%;\"></div>\n      </figure>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </figure>\n   <figure class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack blog-media_media__17gkA blog-video-asset_videoWrapper__RSAt5 geist-show-on-dark-theme\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:center;--stack-justify:center;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:16px\">\n    <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack blog-media_outside__8KjIr blog-video-asset_videoBorder__Kuumi\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"aspect-ratio:1600/900;--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:stretch;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:0px\">\n     <div class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack blog-media_inside__Mq7tv\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:stretch;--stack-justify:flex-start;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:0px\">\n      <figure class=\"video_figure__rlLg4 video_oversize__n2jkl\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--video-margin:0px;--video-width:min(1600px, 950px)\">\n       <div class=\"video_main__8vED4\" style=\"width:100%;\"></div>\n      </figure>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </figure>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">With in-browser code execution, your chatbot can write and run code directly in the browser with WASM and pyodide, without requiring a discrete sandbox setup.</p>\n   <figure class=\"stack_stack__iZkUS stack blog-media_media__17gkA\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--stack-flex:initial;--stack-direction:column;--stack-align:center;--stack-justify:center;--stack-padding:0px;--stack-gap:16px\">\n    <img data-version=\"v1\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"900\" height=\"627\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"image_intrinsic__ulrJk blog-mode-dependent-media_addPadding__lfHNN blog-mode-dependent-media_notScreenshot__QVv9c image_lightMode__SmqSs\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcset=\"https://assets.vercel.com/image/upload/contentful/image/e5382hct74si/3HI1mY7fa6UeEYkKrxSRIg/30cac2af386c3b07645dc9a67a764b50/arch-simple-light.png, https://assets.vercel.com/image/upload/contentful/image/e5382hct74si/3HI1mY7fa6UeEYkKrxSRIg/30cac2af386c3b07645dc9a67a764b50/arch-simple-light.png\" src=\"https://assets.vercel.com/image/upload/contentful/image/e5382hct74si/3HI1mY7fa6UeEYkKrxSRIg/30cac2af386c3b07645dc9a67a764b50/arch-simple-light.png\"><br>\n   </figure>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">The documentation at <a href=\"https://chat-sdk.dev/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">chat-sdk.dev</a> covers everything from project setup and architecture decisions to detailed customization instructions. Learn how to <a href=\"https://chat-sdk.dev/docs/customization/artifacts\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">build your own artifacts</a>, <a href=\"https://chat-sdk.dev/docs/customization/theming\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">customize themes and fonts</a>, <a href=\"https://chat-sdk.dev/docs/customization/testing\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">implement testing strategies</a>, and follow <a href=\"https://chat-sdk.dev/docs/migration-guides/message-parts\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">migration guides</a> as new features are released.</p>\n   <p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\">Whether you're launching a side project or a full-scale enterprise solution, the Chat SDK provides the foundation you need to build incredible chat applications. Check out <a href=\"https://chat-sdk.dev/docs\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-zone=\"null\" class=\"link_link__hbWKh link_highlight__kJZF9\">the docs</a> today to start building with the Chat SDK!</p><p class=\"text_wrapper__i87JK text_paragraph__8ua7M\" data-version=\"v1\" style=\"--text-color:var(--ds-gray-1000);--xs-text-size:1rem;--xs-text-line-height:1.5rem;--xs-text-weight:400;--xs-text-letter-spacing:initial;--sm-text-size:1rem;--sm-text-line-height:1.5rem;--sm-text-weight:400;--sm-text-letter-spacing:initial;--smd-text-size:1rem;--smd-text-line-height:1.5rem;--smd-text-weight:400;--smd-text-letter-spacing:initial;--md-text-size:1rem;--md-text-line-height:1.5rem;--md-text-weight:400;--md-text-letter-spacing:initial;--lg-text-size:1.125rem;--lg-text-line-height:1.5rem;--lg-text-weight:400;--lg-text-letter-spacing:initial\"></p>\n  </div>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "Vercel 发布 Chat SDK，一个基于 Next.js 和 AI SDK 的开源模版，旨在加速聊天机器人应用的开发，并提供生成式 UI 等高级功能。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Vercel 发布 Chat SDK，一个基于 Next.js 和 AI SDK 的开源模版，旨在加速聊天机器人应用的开发，并提供生成式 UI 等高级功能。",
  "summary": "Vercel 发布了 Chat SDK，这是一个免费且开源的模版，旨在帮助开发者构建强大的聊天机器人应用，解决传统聊天机器人开发流程复杂耗时的问题。该 SDK 基于 Next.js 应用路由（App Router）和 Vercel 的 AI SDK。开发者可以使用任何 AI 模型，并能快速部署应用。Chat SDK 具备消息持久化、身份验证、多模态支持和可分享的聊天等基础功能，并提供生成式 UI、自定义组件和浏览器内代码执行等高级特性。开发者可以通过 chat-sdk.dev 上的文档学习如何设置项目、自定义主题和字体、实现测试策略以及进行迁移。Chat SDK 适用于各种规模的项目，从个人项目到企业级解决方案。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Chat SDK：生产级聊天机器人应用模版",
      "explanation": "基于 Next.js 和 AI SDK，Chat SDK 提供了一个完整的应用框架，简化了聊天机器人应用的开发流程。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Chat SDK：支持任意 AI 模型",
      "explanation": "Chat SDK 的灵活性体现在它允许开发者根据自己的需求选择和集成不同的 AI 模型。"
    },
    {
      "point": "生成式 UI：创建动态交互界面",
      "explanation": "通过生成式 UI，开发者可以创建超出简单文本响应的丰富用户体验，界面可以根据对话内容进行调整。"
    },
    {
      "point": "Chat SDK：支持浏览器内代码执行",
      "explanation": "借助 WASM 和 pyodide，聊天机器人可以直接在浏览器中编写和运行代码，无需单独的沙箱环境。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "Chat SDK is a free， open-source template for building powerful chatbot applications.",
    "With generative UI， you can create dynamic， interactive interfaces that go beyond simple text responses， enabling rich user experiences that adapt to the conversation context.",
    "With in-browser code execution， your chatbot can write and run code directly in the browser with WASM and pyodide， without requiring a discrete sandbox setup."
  ],
